data.description: Beautiful Afton open plan contemporary infused with natural light. Abundant windows capture the distant mountain views and professionally landscaped grounds. Hardwood floors, vaulted ceiling, expansive living room with gas fireplace. From the living room 2 double french doors lead to the large wrap around deck with automated awning. The gourmet kitchen features a Viking cooktop and double ovens, Miele dishwasher, plus an oversized walk-in pantry. The conditioned sunroom is great for dining or just enjoying the view while enjoying your favorite beverage. Also on the main level, 2 bedrooms, Jack and Jill full bathroom, office, mud room with a raised dog washing station, powder room and laundry room with utility sink. The second level features a generous lofted primary suite with 2 walk-in closets, soaking tub, separate shower and mountain view’s. The attached 3 car garage with shop has a 2 bedroom apartment above with private entrance. Separate storage building with overhead garage door for your yard and garden equipment. Fiber internet. Covered and fenced area for animals. Fenced yard. Bedroom and bathroom count includes 2 bedroom 1 bathroom apartment. Whole house generator, multi zone heating and cooling.
